    "In providing detailed insight into the data preparation stage, the aim is to enhance the transparency and reproducibility of our approach, thereby facilitating the development of accurate trading strategies in the Bitcoin domain.",
    "Bitcoin price dynamics is influenced by a variety of factors ranging from geopolitical events to regulatory changes, making it an intriguing case for an in-depth study.",
    "The historical price data of Bitcoin offer a rich tapestry of information that serves multiple purposes and reveals patterns that have emerged over the years, which can be instrumental in predicting futures price movements.",
